        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="./images/watch.jpg" alt="" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="./images/shoes.jpg" alt="" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card text-center pb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-dark" >Hello <%= user.username %>,</a >
          <p class="card-text p-3"> 10% Instant discount with select bank credit & debit cards - Buy more, save more! Top brands for electronics, fashion, home & kitchen. Free Shipping on orders above ₹499. Low Prices. Huge Selection. Easy & Fast Delivery. Great Offers. Top Brands. Best Deals. </p>
        </div>
      </div>

